%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Salesforce%20AI%20is%20handling%20customer%20inquiries%20with%2093%25%20accuracy%2C%20Marc%20Benioff%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223543%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Marc%20Benioff%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685d6cbb3d5881a51c1c23f7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222311%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMarc%20Benioff%20has%20AI%20handling%20many%20tasks%20at%20Salesforce.%3Cp%3EAnadolu%2FAnadolu%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarc-benioff%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMarc%20Benioff%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20AI%20at%20Salesforce%20achieves%2093%25%20accuracy%20in%20customer%20interactions.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe're%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bdigital%20labor%20revolution%2C%26quot%3B%20potentially%20worth%20trillions%2C%20Benioff%20says.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BAI%20is%20doing%2030%20to%2050%25%20of%20the%20work%20at%20Salesforce%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMarc%20Benioff%20is%20all%20in%20on%20AI%20at%20Salesforce%2C%20and%20he%20said%20it's%20working%20with%20grade-A%20accuracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2060-year-old%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsalesforce-cuts-diversity-hiring-goals-amid-dei-backlash-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESalesforce%20founder%20and%20CEO%3C%2Fa%3E%20told%20Bloomberg's%20Emily%20Chang%20that%20the%20company%20is%20having%20%26quot%3Bhundreds%20of%20thousands%26quot%3B%20of%20AI%20conversations%20with%20customers%2C%20and%20they%20are%2093%25%20accurate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20for%20a%20large%20brand%20or%20a%20large%20company%20that%20we%20work%20with%2C%20like%20Disney%2C%20it's%20about%2093%25%2C%26quot%3B%20Benioff%20said%20in%20the%20interview%20published%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20Benioff%20told%20investors%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsalesforce-agentforce-ai-tool-automate-tasks-boost-productivity-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAgentforce%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Salesforce's%20platform%20for%20building%20AI%20agents%2C%20was%20seeing%20%26quot%3Bamazing%20results%26quot%3B%20in%20resolving%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20customer%20service%20queries.%20It%20allows%20%26quot%3Bhuman%20employees%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20most%20nuanced%20issues%20and%20customer%20relationships%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20ethics%20of%20AI%20potentially%20replacing%20human%20roles%2C%20Benioff%20said%20it's%20a%20%26quot%3Bdigital%20labor%20revolution%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20could%20pay%20off%20in%20the%20trillions.%20However%2C%20it's%20on%20CEOs%20to%20make%20sure%20their%20%26quot%3Bvalues%20are%20in%20the%20right%20place.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBenioff%20told%20Chang%20that%20we're%20looking%20at%20the%20deployment%20of%20an%20estimated%20%243%20trillion%20to%20%2412%20trillion%20of%20digital%20labor.%20That%20labor%20could%20look%20like%20AI%20agents%20or%20robots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20is%20doing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsalesforce-marc-benioff-ai-half-work-layoffs-employees-question-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E30%20to%2050%25%20of%20the%20work%20%3C%2Fa%3Eat%20Salesforce%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20technology%20is%20supporting%20%26quot%3Bkey%20functions%20like%20engineering%2C%20coding%2C%20support.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESalesforce%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecent-company-layoffs-laying-off-workers-2025%23salesforce-is-cutting-more-than-1-000-jobs-33%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecutting%20more%20than%201%2C000%20jobs%20in%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20Bloomberg%20earlier%20reported.%20The%20company%20had%20about%207