est%20surrounding%20arrests%20and%20deportations%3B%20or%20increasingly%20hot%20and%20violent%20wildfires%2C%20tornadoes%2C%20and%20hurricanes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20military%20uses%20the%20acronym%20OBE%2C%20or%20%26quot%3Bovercome%20by%20events%2C%26quot%3B%20when%20circumstances%20spiral%20out%20of%20control%20and%20beyond%20the%20scope%20of%20a%20mission's%20plan%20and%20preparation.%20Chad%20Huddleston%2C%20an%20anthropology%20professor%20at%20Southern%20Illinois%20University%20Edwardsville%20who%20has%20studied%20prepper%20communities%20for%20more%20than%20a%20decade%2C%20said%20that%20may%20describe%20how%20Americans%20are%20feeling%20about%20recent%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20looking%20in%20their%20immediate%20area%20to%20see%20what's%20going%20on%20with%20that%20to%20determine%2C%20'Well%2C%20what%20should%20I%20be%20worried%20about%3F'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuddleston%20started%20following%20preppers%20back%20in%202008%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewhen%20the%20phenomenon%20was%20becoming%20more%20mainstream.%20He%20found%20that%20the%20events%20that%20motivated%20people%20to%20start%20prepping%20then%20weren't%20the%209%2F11%20attacks%20or%20subsequent%20wars%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20something%20closer%20to%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20all%20said%20Katrina%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20Katrina%20happened%2C%20they%20could%20watch%20on%20TV%20all%20these%20people%20suffering.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20like%2C%20'Oh%20no%2C%20that%20could%20happen%20here%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20TikTokers%20posting%20about%20a%20possible%20World%20War%20III%20this%20week%2C%20one%20user%20shared%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40fabireyezz23%2Fvideo%2F7519968872175258935%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evideo%3C%2Fa%3E%20showing%20how%20to%20build%20a%20survival%20kit%20for%20less%20than%20%2420%20at