t%20returns%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225579%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Engineers'%20Gate%20entrance%20in%20Central%20Park%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685d80f3f748d8c055f46f21%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223719%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECarlo%20Allegri%2FREUTERS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EEngineers%20Gate%20is%20surging%2C%20with%20assets%20and%20head%20count%20doubling%20since%202024.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20fund%20is%20up%2012%25%20this%20year%2C%20continuing%20a%20streak%20of%20double-digit%20returns.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20prescient%20external%20investment%20in%20quant%20startup%20TwinBeech%20helped%20buoy%20performance%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFive%20years%20ago%2C%20quant%20hedge%20fund%20Engineers%20Gate%20was%20reeling%20%E2%80%94%20from%20poor%20returns%2C%20investor%20redemptions%2C%20and%20the%20ignominious%20departure%20of%20its%20founder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20fortunes%20look%20different%20these%20days.%20The%20fund%20is%20now%20firmly%20in%20growth%20mode%2C%20preoccupied%20with%20deploying%20%244%20billion%20in%20assets%20to%20a%20growing%20roster%20of%20portfolio%20managers%20and%20keeping%20a%20performance%20hot%20streak%20rolling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEngineers%20Gate%20is%20up%20about%2012%25%20through%20the%20end%20of%20May%2C%20according%20to%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20performance.%20That%20tops%20the%202%25%20composite%20gain%20among%20hedge%20funds%20and%20the%207.9%25%20gain%20among%20equity%20quant%20funds%2C%20according%20to%20hedge%20fund%20analytics%20firm%20PivotalPath's%20index%20data%20through%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fund%20posted%20double-digit%20gains%20in%202023%20and%202024%20as%20well%2C%20returning%2013.6%25%20and%2010.5%25%2C%20respectively%2C%20a%20person%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesman%20for%20the%20firm%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20portfolio%20manager%20roster%20has%20more%20than%20doubled%20since%20the%20start%20of%202024%2C%20growing%20from%2030%20to%20more%20than%2075%20today%2C%20people%20familiar%20said.%20It%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fengineers-gate-quant-expanding-asia-singapore-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexpanded%20to%20Singapore%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year%2C%20appointing%20Rafael%20Andreata%20and%20Mingyan%20Huang%20to%20lead%20their%20Asia%20Pacific%20build%20out%2C%20Business%20Insider%20previously%20reported.%20In%20January%2C%20ex-Schonfeld%20PM%20Mike%20Daylamani%20joined%20to%20launch%20a%20fundamental%20investing%20business%2C%20expanding%20beyond%20Engineers'%20systematic%20trading%20roots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20rapid%20growth%20at%20multimanager%20hedge%20funds%20doesn't%20necessarily%20correlate%20to%20sustained%20investment%20performance%2C%20and%20in%20many%20cases%2C%20the%20opposite%20has%20happened%20%E2%80%94%20brisk%20buildouts%20have%20led%20to%20retrenchment%20at%20firms%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fschonfeld-hedge-fund-ryan-tolkin-grapple-with-poor-returns-departures-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elike%20Schonfeld%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Eisler%2C%20and%20Brevan%20Howard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20progress%20marks%20a%20sharp%20turn%20from%202020%2C%20when%20poor%20performance%20and%20revelations%20about%20founder%20Glenn%20Dubin's%20ties%20to%20convicted%20sex%20offender%20Jeffrey%20Epstein%20spurred%20investor%20exits.%20That%20year%2C%20Dubin%20sold%20his%20stake%20in%20the%20firm%20he%20launched%20in%202014%20and%20was%20replaced%20by%20longtime%20deputy%20Greg%20Eisner%2C%20who%20remains%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20shore%20up%20capital%2C%20Blackstone%20Group%20filled%20the%20void%20left%20by%20anchor%20investor%20Canada%20Pension%20Plan%20Investment%20Board%2C%20as%20Bloomberg%20reported%20at%20the%20time%2C%20accounting%20for%20the%20bulk%20of%20Engineers'%20%241%20billion%20in%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20gains%20of%2011%25%20in%202020%20and%2025%25%20in%202021%2C%20hedge%20fund%20giants%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2022-02-16%2Fmillennium-point72-discuss-bids-for-quant-fund-engineers-gate%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMillennium%20and%20Point72%3C%2Fa%3E%20separately%20explored%20acquiring%20the%20fund%20in%202022%2C%20though%20a%20buyout%20didn't%20materialize.%20Blackstone%20ended%20up%20selling%20its%20stake%20in%20Engineers%20Gate%20at%20the%20end%20of%20that%20year%2C%20and%20Millennium%2C%20which%20has%20become%20one%20of%20the%20top%20investors%20in%20other%20hedge%20funds%20via%20separately%20managed%20accounts%2C%20allocated%20%241%20billion%20to%20the%20firm%2C%20according%20to%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStephen%20Owen%2C%20who%20joined%20in%202014%20and%20holds%20the%20title%20of%20chief%20architect%20and%20founding%20PM%2C%20according%20to%20his%20LinkedIn%20page%2C%20and%20Gavin%20Boyle%2C%20who%20joined%20in%202017%20and%20leads%20the%20London%20office%2C%20have%20been%20significant%20contributors%20to%20the%20fund's%20performance%2C%20people%20familiar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20key%20move%20for%20Engineers%20Gate%20was%20its%20own%20prescient%20investment%20in%20an%20external%20hedge%20fund.%20The%20firm%20seeded%20quant%20startup%20TwinBeech%20Capital%2C%20which%20former%20Cubist%20PM%20Jinghua%20Yan%20launched%20in%202019.%20It's%20been%20one%20of%20the%20best-performing%20new%20launches%20in%20years%2C%20according%20to%20several%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwinBeech%20stumbled%20in%202024%2C%20but%20has%20consistently%20delivered%20high%20double-digit%20returns%2C%20the%20people%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwinBeech%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2