eo%20games%20from%20the%201980s%20and%20early%201990s%2C%20and%20said%20that%20AI%20is%20actually%20in%20its%20%26quot%3Binfancy.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BIt's%20Pac-Man%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20ain't%20even%20Halo%20yet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20point%20was%20that%20early%20video%20games%20required%20a%20level%20of%20imagination%20from%20the%20player%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20sophisticated%20graphics%20and%20a%20real%20story.%20He%20said%20this%20same%20level%20of%20imagination%20is%20needed%20from%20%26quot%3Bthe%20people%20that%20love%20AI%2C%20the%20folks%20whose%20imagination%20is%20doing%20the%20work%20as%20you're%20training%20it%20or%20it's%20learning%20from%20your%20imagination.%26quot%3B%20He%20added%20that%20AI%20will%20not%20stifle%20creativity%2C%20but%20provide%20room%20to%20enhance%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWill.i.am%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20role%20and%20need%20for%20AI%20in%20higher%20education.%20Through%20a%20partnership%20with%20Arizona%20State%20University%2C%20FYI.ai%20will%20provide%20technology%20to%20help%20enhance%20the%20learning%20experience%20and%20prepare%20students%20for%20the%20reality%20that%20awaits%20them%20upon%20graduation%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20go%20out%20into%20the%20world%2C%20you're%20not%20just%20competing%20with%20humans%2C%26quot%3B%20Will.i.am%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20today's%20students.%20Rather%2C%20he%20said%2C%20there's%20an%20%26quot%3Bonslaught%20of%20agents%26quot%3B%20that%20are%20replacing%20the%20jobs%20students%20are%20going%20to%20school%20for%20%E2%80%94%20and%20no%20one%20is%20trying%20to%20help%20them%20compete.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWill.i.am%20said%20FYI.Ai%20is%20going%20to%20provide%20a%20path%20so%20that%20students%20can%20build%20an%20AI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgenerative-ai-evolution-software-companies-develop-ai-agents-workforce-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eagent%3C%2Fa%3