%20physicist%20in%20the%20family.%20To%20my%20most%20cherished%20friend%2C%20Jes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStaley%20maintained%20a%20relationship%20with%20Epstein%20after%20he%20left%20JP%20Morgan%20and%20confided%20in%20him%20while%20Barclays%20recruited%20him%20for%20the%20CEO%20role%2C%20which%20he%20held%20for%20six%20years%2C%20emails%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20never%20wavered%20in%20our%20friendship%20these%20last%20three%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Staley%20wrote%20to%20Epstein%20in%20October%202015%2C%20as%20he%20was%20interviewing%20to%20lead%20the%20multinational%20bank.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EContrary%20to%20Staley's%20claims%2C%20he%20and%20Epstein%20were%20in%20contact%20over%20many%20years%2C%20including%20indirectly%20in%202016%20and%202017%2C%20the%20Financial%20Conduct%20Authority%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr%20Staley%20chose%20to%20take%20a%20calculated%20risk%20that%20we%20would%20take%20his%20inaccurate%20account%20of%20his%20relationship%20with%20Mr%20Epstein%20at%20face%20value%2C%26quot%3B%20Therese%20Chambers%2C%20joint%20executive%20director%20of%20enforcement%20and%20market%20oversight%20at%20the%20FCA%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20hoped%20that%20the%20truth%20would%20never%20come%20to%20light%20and%20that%20he%20would%20get%20away%20with%20it.%20Such%20a%20serious%20lack%20of%20integrity%20flies%20in%20the%20face%20of%20the%20requirements%20we%20place%20on%20those%20at%20the%20top%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tribunal%20slashed%20the%20FCA's%20fine%20to%20%C2%A31.1%20million.%20The%20reduction%20accounted%20for%20deferred%20shares%20that%20Barclays%20didn't%20allow%20him%20to%20receive%2C%20the%20ruling%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjes-staley-barclays-ceo-financial-services-ban-upheld-jeffrey-epstein-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22p