%20be%20pretty%20good%2C%20right%3F%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETurns%20out%20%E2%80%A6%20it%20is.%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20could%20taste%20a%20blend%20of%20minerals%20that%20managed%20to%20give%20the%20water%20a%20subtle%20richness.%20It%20felt%20elevated%20%E2%80%94%20as%20much%20as%20water%20can%20feel%20elevated%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20really%20enjoyed%20it.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EEssentia%20%E2%80%94%20%240.08%20per%20ounce%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bottle%20of%20Essentia%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685c4e963d5881a51c1c13d5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20water%20from%20Essentia%20had%20a%20sleek%20look.%20%3Cp%3ESteven%20John%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20paid%20%242.69%20for%20a%2033.8-ounce%20bottle%20of%20Essentia%2C%20which%20calls%20itself%20the%20%26quot%3B%231%20ionized%20alkaline%20water%26quot%3B%20right%20on%20the%20bottle%20and%20notes%20that%20it%20has%20electrolytes%20and%20a%20%26quot%3B9.5pH%20or%20higher.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20curious%20about%20the%20mention%20of%20pH%20on%20the%20bottle.%20The%20pH%20scale%20ranges%20from%200%20to%2014%20and%20measures%20how%20acidic%20or%20alkaline%20a%20solution%20is%2C%20with%207%20being%20neutral%20and%2014%20being%20highly%20alkaline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20isn't%20much%20scientific%20evidence%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.webmd.com%2Fdiet%2Fwhat-is-alkaline-water%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrinking%20higher%20alkaline%20water%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20any%20major%20health%20benefits%2C%20though%20water%20with%20a%20pH%20level%20below%20or%20above%207%20might%20have%20a%20bitter%20taste.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEssentia's%20water%20tasted%20ever%20so%20slightly%20sweet%2C%20albeit%20with%20a%20hint%20of%20bitterness.%20Not%20a%20negative%20hint%20of%20bitterness%2C%20just%20a%20semi-pleasant%20whisper%20of%20it.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv