n%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20paid%20%242.79%20for%20a%2016.9-ounce%20bottle%20of%20Waiakea%20water%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20the%20priciest%20option%20per%20ounce%20on%20this%20list.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDescribed%20by%20the%20brand%20as%20%26quot%3Bpremium%20Hawaiian%20volcanic%20water%2C%26quot%3B%20this%20variety%20comes%20from%20a%20well%20source%20at%20the%20base%20of%20a%20volcano.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20simple%20terms%2C%20it%20starts%20as%20melted%20snow%20and%20rain%20that%20filters%20through%20porous%20volcanic%20rock%20and%20later%20re-emerges%20as%20naturally%20alkaline%20water%20with%20a%20a%20pH%20ranging%20from%207.6%20to%208.2.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnyway%2C%20despite%20the%20cool-sounding%20origin%20of%20this%20water%2C%20it%20was%20my%20least%20favorite%20of%20the%20bunch.%20I%20couldn't%20detect%20much%20of%20a%20mineral%20profile%20and%20it%20tasted%20vaguely%20like%20plastic%20to%20me.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPoland%20Spring%20-%20%240.10%20per%20ounce%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bottle%20of%20Poland%20Spring%20water%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685c4e96f748d8c055f45bd7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI've%20had%20many%20bottles%20of%20Poland%20Spring%20in%20my%20lifetime.%20%3Cp%3ESteven%20John%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20bought%20a%2020-ounce%20bottle%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhich-brand-has-best-lime-sparkling-water-seltzer-grocery-store-ranking%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPoland%20Spring%20water%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20%242.09.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20water%20originally%20came%20from%20the%20springs%20in%20Poland%2C%20Maine%2C%20but%20is%20now%20sourced%20from%20other%20springs.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20drinking%20Poland%20Spring%20water%20for%20years%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20think%20I've%20ever%20done%20it%20with%20great%20intention%20or%20presence%20of%20mind.%20This%20time%2C%20I%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20what%20I%20found%20was%20an%20H2O%20that%20was%20about%20as%20refreshingly%20flavorless%20as%20water%20gets.%20I%20detected%20no%20real%20flavor%20profile%20beyond%20that%20pleasant%20neutrality%20of%2C%20you%20know%2C%20water.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20I'm%20not%20surprised%20this%20is%20such%20a%20popular%20go-to%20for%20so%20many%20people%20I%20know.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI'd%20readily%20go%20back%20to%20most%20of%20the%20waters%20on%20this%20list%2C%20but%20Fiji%20impressed%20me%20most.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Group%20of%20water%20bottles%20on%20counter%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685c4e963d5881a51c1c13d2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20water%20I%20like%20most%20may%20not%20be%20your%20favorite%20pick%2C%20but%20I'd%20say%20all%20these%20varieties%20are%20worth%20trying%20just%20in%20case%20you%20like%20them%20more%20than%20I%20did.%20%3Cp%3ESteven%20John%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20my%20taste-testing%20(if%20one%20can%20call%20it%20that%20when%20sipping%20water)%2C%20I%20was%20well-hydrated%20and%20not%20at%20all%20thirsty.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20in%20all%2C%20Fiji%20was%20my%20top%20pick.%20I%20was%20struck%20that%20it%20actually%20lived%20up%20to%20its%20hype.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20also%20surprised%20to%20find%20that%20a%20basic%20brand%20like%20Poland%20Spring%20cost%20me%20more%20per%20ounce%20than%20Fiji%20water.%20Although%20prices%20can%20widely%20vary%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20when%20buying%20in%20bulk%20%E2%80%94%20this%20realization%20made%20the%20more%20elevated%2C%20premium%20stuff%20feel%20less%20out%20of%20reach.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20buy%20most%20of%20these%20waters%20again%20except%20for%20Waiakea%20because%20I%20didn't%20care%20for%20the%20taste%20especially%20at%20its%20high%20per-ounce%20p